body:
„Karma is a bitch.“

Character/Pairing: Tony Stark x fem!Reader

Fandom: Marvel Cinematic Universe

Words: 671

—–

Place: the maybe least visited, oldest and most rundown bar in Malibu. 

The actors: you as the owner and barkeeper and.. Tony Stark. 

Goddamn Iron Man stood in the entrance of your bar and stared you down! „You don’t have a lot of clients, eh?“, he asked with a smirk, came in and took the seat right in front of you at the counter. You snickered. „Nah, today came the new Iron Man merchandise and they all went shopping. What can I do for you, Mr. Stark?“  He threw some money on the wooden board. „Whiskey. A lot. And I need someone who doesn’t treat me like a special snowflake.“ Now, you had to laugh and poured not just your customer, but also yourself a drink. You raised your glass to him and smiled widely. „Good, I was never one for ‘Mister’ and 'Sir’ anyway.Feel free to stay for a while.“ The glasses clanked and both of you took a sip. „So..“, Tony started. „Since you seem to be the owner of this sinkhole I assume you are Y/N?“ You looked surprised at him and wanted to ask where he got your name from, but he pointed at his phone with a grin. Ah, good old Google.. „So, Y/N.. Are you one of those barkeepers who listen to whatever sorrow their customers need to talk about?“, he asked. „Not really.“, you answered quickly and with the most stern face you were capable of. „But lets make an exception for a special snowflake. Deal?“ He grimaced, but then you heard him chuckle. „Sassy and owns a bar. I think you are my new best friend now.“ You sighted over-theatrically: „Gods, why? Why me?“ He emptied his glass. „Because Karma is a bitch, darling.“ 

You winked at him. „When someone knows this, it’s you. Heard about New York in the news.“Tony rolled his eyes, but started to talk. You were used to listening to customers, because that’s what every single barkeeper on the planet does. But you had to admit that this one, this „superhero“, was entirely different. It took no long time for him to open up to you and soon, he was telling you things you were sure he doesn’t tell anyone else. But he also wanted to hear about you! So you told him everything he asked for: about your past, your hobbies, how you got the bar and even more. It was very late when he suddenly said: „It’s truly a shame we haven’t met sooner. I really think we would have been great friends.“ You smiled widely. „Umh.. Better late than never, right?“ Tony laughed. 

A true, happy and real laugh. „I was hoping for you to say that, Y/N. Gotta go now, but you need to visit me one day so I can introduce you to J.A.R.V.I.S.! You will hear from me soon, dear.“ 

He shook your hand and then, he was gone.Days over days gone by and you haven’t heard anything from your new friend. Actually, you started to believe Tony wasn’t serious about you visiting him or anything. You knew you could just drive to the villa and just say hi, but you were too shy. You needed to see him one more time first. Right when you decided to finally give up your hopes, you heard two voices coming from the entrance. „What are we doing here, Tony? This place looks like trash!“, said one of them. Then you saw Tony Starks back as he talked to the other man. „But the owner isn’t, Rhodes! I want you to meed Y/N, the frist person after you who doesn’t think I’m totally crazy.“ You smiled at the two as they came to you to take a seat. Tonys companion offered you a hand. „I’m the other friend, James Rhodes. My condolences, it’s impossible to get rid of him now.“ Tony grinned at both of you. „This is the start of something wonderful. And not just because of the booze, Rhodey.“

body:

by DayDreamBeliever277

Eddie and Venom decide to move back to New York. After the incident with the Life Foundation, Eddie longs for anonymity. What better place to disappear in then a big city? One where time never stands still. Hero’s grow and villains come and go. New York is still enthralled with the big fight between the Avengers. But all those hero’s keep attracting problems. Follow Eddie en Venom on their journey to a quiet life?
